quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,Ndayidde empewo ezifumuula enfuufu olufumuula
  51,2,Olwo nno nendayira ebire ebyetikka enkuba olwetikka
  51,3,N'amaato agaseeyeeya mu mazzi mu bwangu
  51,4,Era ndayidde Malayika ezigabanya Riziki okusinziira ku kiragiro ekiba kiziweereddwa
  51,5,Mazima bye mulaganyisibwa bya kutuukirira
  51,6,Era ddala olunaku lwo kusasula lwa kubaawo
  51,7,Ndayidde eggulu eryakolebwa mu ngeri ennungi
  51,8,Mazima mmwe muli mu kigambo ekyawukamu (temussa kimu ku bikwata ku Kur’ani)
  51,9,Awugulwa ku kyo oyo eyabuzibwa (natakkiriza)
  51,10,Baakolimirwa abo abalimba (aboogera ebitali bituufu ku Nabbi)
  51,11,Abo abali mu nnyanga ey’obukaafiiri nga babulubuuta
  51,12,Nga babuuza nti olunaku lwo kusasula luliba lwaddi
  51,13,Lwe lunaku bo lwe balyokebwa omuliro
  51,14,"(Nga bwe bagambibwa nti) mukombe ebibonerezo bya mmwe, kino kyekyo kye mwagambanga nti kibatuusibweko mu bwangu"
  51,15,Mazima abatya Katonda balibeera mu masamba nga mulimu n'ensulo za mazzi
  51,16,Nga beeyanza ebyo Mukama omulabirizi waabwe byalibawa (anti) mazima bo oluberyeberye lwekyo bali balongoosa
  51,17,Bebakanga e kiseera kitono mu kiro
  51,18,Ate nga mu ttumbi babanga mu kwe gayirira
  51,19,Era nga mu maali yaabwe mulimu omugabo gwo musabi nooyo atafuna kimumala (naye nga tasaba)
  51,20,"Era mu nsi mulimu obubonero (obulaga okubaayo kwa Katonda n’obuyinza bwe), eri abo abakkiriza obukkiriza obwa nnamaddala"
  51,21,Ne mu mmwe mwennyini (mulimu obubonero) abaffe temulaba
  51,22,Ne muggulu y'eri riziki za mmwe na byonna bye mulagaanyisibwa
  51,23,"Kale ndayidde Mukama omulabirizi we ggulu n'ensi, nti ekyo bwekityo bwekiri (era nga ekyo buli muntu yenna akimanyi) nga bwe mumanyi nti mwatula"
  51,24,Abaffe ebikwata ku bagenyi ba Ibrahim abekitiibwa bya kutuukako
  51,25,"Bwe baayingira weyali ne bagamba nti mirembe, (naye) naagamba nti mirembe (wabula muli) bantu abatamanyiddwa"
  51,26,Olwo nno nadda eri abantu be naleeta ennyana y'ente ensava (enjokye)
  51,27,Nagibasembereza naagamba nti abaffe nga temuulye
  51,28,"(Bwe bataalya) yawulira nga abatiddemu, ne bagamba nti totya era nebamuwa amawulire agessanyu ag'omwana omulenzi omumanyi ennyo"
  51,29,"(Awo wennyini) mukyala we naatuuka nga ayogerera waggulu nakuba ekyenyi kye, era naagamba nti (nze nga ndi) mukadde omugumba (nzaala ntya)"
  51,30,"(Ba Malayika) ne bagamba nti bwekityo Mukama omulabirizi wo bwagambye anti mazima yye bulijjo, ye mugoba nsonga omumanyi ennyo"
  51,31,"Ibrahim naagamba nti, ate mmwe ababaka nsonga ki ebaleese"
  51,32,Nebagamba nti mazima ffe tutumiddwa eri abantu abonoonyi
  51,33,Tube nga tubayiwako amayinja agomu bbumba ejjokye
  51,34,"Nga malambe okuva ewa Mukama omulabirizi wo, nga ga (kuzikiriza) abonoonyi abasukkiridde"
  51,35,(Katonda agamba) awo nno twagyamu oyo yenna eyakirimu (ekitundu ekyo) mu bakkiriza
  51,36,Naye tetwasangamu okugyako e nyumba emu eyabasiraamu
  51,37,Era twaleka mu kyo ekyo kuyiga eri abo abatya ebibonerezo ebiruma ennyo
  51,38,Era ne Musa (alimu ekyo kuyiga) bwe twamutuma ewa Firawo n’obujulizi obweyolefu
  51,39,Yagaana (okugoberera Musa) olwokwesigula abali emabega we era nagamba nti (Musa) mulogo oba mulalu
  51,40,Olwo nno netumukwatako ne ggye rye netubakasuka mu nnyanja nga naye anenyezebwa
  51,41,Ne mu Bantu ba Aadi (mulimu ekyokuyiga) bwe twabasindikira empewo engumba (etaliimu mukisa tereeta nkuba wadde okuwasisa ebibala)
  51,42,Nga tereka kintu kyonna kyeyitako okugyako nga ekifuula nga ensaano
  51,43,Ne mu bantu ba Thamud (mulimu ekyokuyiga) bwe bagambibwa nti mweyagale okumala akaseera katono
  51,44,"Wabula bo basukka ekiragiro kya Mukama omulabiririzi waabwe, olwo nno okubwatuka okwamaanyi ne kubatuukako nga nabo balaba"
  51,45,Tebaasobola kusituka (badduke) era tebaali ba kuwona
  51,46,N'abantu ba Nuhu nga bano tebannabaawo (nabo balimu ekyokuyiga anti nabo baazikirizibwa era nabo kya bagwanira) anti mazima bo baali bantu abonoonyi
  51,47,(N'ebirala ebirimu ekyokuyiga) ne ggulu twalizimba n'obuyinza (bwaffe) era mazima tukyaligaziya
  51,48,"N'ensi twagiseteeza, ddala nga ffe abatesiteesi abasinga"
  51,49,Era twatonda mu buli kintu emitindo ebiri ebiri (ekisajja ne kikazi) oba olyawo ne mujjukira
  51,50,Kale mudduke mudde eri Katonda mazima nze ndi mutiisa owolwatu gye muli okuva gyali
  51,51,"N’olwekyo temussanga ku Katonda ebisinzibwa ebirala, mazima nze ndi mutiisa owolwatu gye muli okuva gyali"
  51,52,Bwekityo abo ababakulembera tewali mubaka yabajjira okugyako nga bagamba nti mulogo oba mulalu
  51,53,Abaffe bakyeramira (nedda ssi bwekiri) wabula bo bantu be wagguzi
  51,54,Kale baveeko toli ggwe anenyezebwa
  51,55,Wabula bulirira anti mazima okubulirira kugasa abakkiriza
  51,56,Era ssaatonda amajinni n’abantu wabula lwakuba nti bansinze
  51,57,Sibaagalamu Riziki era ssaagala bandiise
  51,58,Mazima Katonda yye yaagaba Riziki nannyini maanyi omusobozi
  51,59,Mazima abo abeeyisa obubi balina ebyonoono nga ebyonoono bya bannaabwe n’olwekyo tebampapya (kubatuusaako bibonerezo mu bwangu)
  51,60,Okubonabona kuli eri abo abawakanya olunaku lwabwe olwo lwe baalaganyisibwa (olunaku lw’enkomerero)